name: Stardict-quick-achinese
tagline: Stardict package for Achinese dictionary of foreign words
body:
Stardict Quick package for Achinese dictionary of foreign words

This is autogenerated dictionary for StarDict.

Data were downloaded from following website:

<https://l10n-indonesian.alioth.debian.org/pub/stardict/quick>

The original source is available under GPL-3.

Install dictionary by copying dictionary files to dic/ folder in StarDict.
On Linux it is usually /usr/share/stardict/dic/
on Windows C:\Program files\stardict\dic\.

Original description of dictionary:

 Redrafted to StarDict by KPLI - Aceh, Ar-Ros and BlankOn Aceh.
 .
 Taken from the dictionary database Aceh-Indonesia e-Cesia young lecturer Unsyiah research results.
 .
 Thanks to the research team (Viska Mutiawani, Juwita, Irvanizam and all those involved in this dictionary research)
 .
 Copyright (c)  2012-2016 Mahyuddin <yudi.al@gmail.com>, Viska Mutiawani, Juwita, Irvanizam

 A copy of the license is included in the section entitled "GNU General Public License".
 .
 Encoding: ISO 639-3
 .
 Warranty: It is not guaranteed that the translations in this package are accurate.
 No warrantee is made for usefulness of this package, and the authors accepts no responsibility for any

 .
